      "title": "系统架构概览",
      "doc_type": "design",
      "status": "published",
      "content": "灵镜 (LingPrism) 是企业知识与代码智能平台。技术栈：Next.js 前端三端、Node GraphQL API、Go Core、Rust Indexer、Python AI Worker/MCP。数据层包含 MySQL、Redis、Neo4j、Qdrant、OpenSearch。索引流水线：Git clone → tree-sitter 解析 → Qdrant 向量 + Neo4j 图谱。",
      "indexed_in_search": true
    },
    {
      "id": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000022",
      "knowledge_base_id": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000020",
      "title": "本地开发与 Docker 部署",
      "doc_type": "ops",
      "status": "published",
      "content": "本地开发：pnpm install → docker compose 启动数据层 → migrate + seed + bootstrap → 分别启动 api/core/ai-worker 与前端。Docker 全栈：cd infra/docker && docker compose --profile app up -d --build，统一从 http://localhost:8080 访问。开发账户 admin@lingprism.local / employee@lingprism.local，密码 lingprism123。",
      "indexed_in_search": true
    }
